{\listtext	3.	}This progression of descent from order into chaos, and ascent back into order imply the presence of some kind of gatekeeper. This gatekeeper is present at the protagonist\'92s final departure from order.\
{\listtext	4.	}The gatekeeper often required a fee for passage. \
